text=\"ια\" data-n=\"65\" data-lemma=\"ια\">ΙΑ</span></span>·<span data-text=\"ἡμέρας\" data-n=\"75\" data-lemma=\"ἡμέρα\">Η</span>·<span class=\"supraline\" title=\"line above\"><span data-text=\"ιηε\" data-n=\"85\" data-lemma=\"ιε\">ΗΕ</span></span>·<span data-type=\"persname\" data-name-type=\"attested\" data-text=\"Ἰούλι\n                    ος · Γερμᾶνος\"><span data-type=\"name\" data-name-type=\"\" data-text=\"Ἰούλι\n                    ος\"><span data-text=\"Ἰούλι\n                    ος\" data-n=\"95\" data-lemma=\"Ἰούλιος\">ΙΟ[...]<br id=\"al4-diplomatic\"><span class=\"linenumber\">4</span><span class=\"underline\">ΟΣ</span></span></span><span class=\"underline\">·</span><span data-type=\"name\" data-name-type=\"\" data-text=\"Γερμᾶνος\"><span data-text=\"Γερμᾶνος\" data-n=\"105\" data-lemma=\"Γερμᾶνος\"><span class=\"underline\">Γ</span>ΕΡΜΑ<span class=\"underline\">ΝΟΣ</span></span></span></span><span class=\"underline\">·</span><span data-text=\"γλυκυτά\n                    τῃ\" data-n=\"115\" data-lemma=\"γλυκύς\"><span class=\"underline\">ΓΛΥΚΥΤΑ</span><br id=\"al5-diplomatic\"><span class=\"linenumber\">5</span><span class=\"underline\">ΤΗ</span></span><span data-text=\"θυγατρὶ\" data-n=\"120\" data-lemma=\"θυγάτηρ\"><span class=\"underline\">Θ</span>ΥΓΑΤ<span class=\"underline\">ΡΙ</span></span><span data-text=\"ἐποίησεν\" data-n=\"125\" data-lemma=\"ποιέω\"><span class=\"underline\">ΕΠΟΙΗ</span>[...]</span></span></div><p class=\"miniapp\">l.3 ι</p></div><div class=\"attribution\">Text encoding: Victoria Fendel, Robert Crellin</div><div id=\"edition-diplomatic-simple-lemmatized\"><div class=\"textpart\"><span class=\"ab\" id=\"div-diplomatic\"><span data-text=\"Ἰουλία\" data-n=\"5\" data-lemma=\"Ἰουλία\">ΙΟΥΛΙΑ</span><span data-text=\"Γερμᾶνα\" data-n=\"10\" data-lemma=\"Γερμᾶνα\">ΓΕΡΜΑΝΑ</span><span data-text=\"ἡ\" data-n=\"20\" data-lemma=\"ὁ\">Η</span><span data-text=\"θεοφιλὴς\" data-n=\"25\" data-lemma=\"θεοφιλής\">ΘΕΟΦΙΛΗΣ</span><span data-text=\"ἔζησεν\" data-n=\"30\" data-lemma=\"ζάω\">ΕΖΗΣΕΝ</span><span data-text=\"ἔτη\" data-n=\"35\" data-lemma=\"ἔτος\">ΕΤΗ</span><span data-text=\"ιδ\" data-n=\"45\" data-lemma=\"ιδ\">ΙΔ</span><span data-text=\"μῆνας\" data-n=\"55\" data-lemma=\"μείς\">ΜΗΝΑΣ</span><span data-text=\"ια\" data-n=\"65\" data-lemma=\"ια\">ΙΑ</span><span data-text=\"ἡμέρας\" data-n=\"75\" data-lemma=\"ἡμέρα\">ΗΜΕΡΑΣ</span><span data-text=\"ιε\" data-n=\"85\" data-lemma=\"ιε\">ΙΕ</span><span data-text=\"Ἰούλιος\" data-n=\"95\" data-lemma=\"Ἰούλιος\">ΙΟΥΛΙΟΣ</span><span data-text=\"Γερμᾶνος\" data-n=\"105\" data-lemma=\"Γερμᾶνος\">ΓΕΡΜΑΝΟΣ</span><span data-text=\"γλυκυτάτῃ\" data-n=\"115\" data-lemma=\"γλυκύς\">ΓΛΥΚΥΤΑΤΗ</span><span data-text=\"θυγατρὶ\" data-n=\"120\" data-lemma=\"θυγάτηρ\">ΘΥΓΑΤΡΙ</span><span data-text=\"ἐποίησεν\" data-n=\"125\" data-lemma=\"ποιέω\">ΕΠΟΙΗΣΕΝ</span></span></div><p class=\"miniapp\"></p></div></div>  <div id=\"facsimile-images\"><h2>Facsimile Images</h2><a href=\"ISic001303_tiled.tif\"><img title=\"I.Sicily with the permission of the Assessorato Regionale dei Beni Culturali e dell’Identità Siciliana - Dipartimento dei Beni Culturali e dell’Identità Siciliana\" src=\"ISic001303_tiled-thumb.tif\"></a><a href=\"ISic001303.jpg\"><img title=\"I.Sicily with the permission of the Assessorato Regionale dei Beni Culturali e dell’Identità Siciliana - Dipartimento dei Beni Culturali e dell’Identità Siciliana\" src=\"ISic001303-thumb.jpg\"></a></div>  <div id=\"apparatus\"><h4>Apparatus criticus</h4><ul><li><span>  <span>Text based on photographs and Kaibel's transcription</span>  </span>; </li><li><span class=\"line 3\">line.3: <span>lapis, Ferrara, Kaibel: ΗΕ; Kaibel: η⟨ε⟩ (i.e. suppressed the E); Korhonen: ιε (or κε)</span>  </span></li></ul></div>  <div id=\"translation\"><h2>English translation</h2><p class=\"translation-author\"><a href=\"https://orcid.org/0000-0001-5187-5163\">Marta Fogagnolo</a></p>  <p>Ioulia Germana, dear to the gods, lived for 14 years, 11 months and 15 days. Ioulios Germanos made this for his sweetest daughter.</p>  </div>  <div id=\"translation\"><h2>Italian translation</h2><p class=\"translation-author\"><a href=\"https://orcid.org/0000-0001-5187-5163\">Marta Fogagnolo</a></p>  <p>Ioulia Germana, cara agli dèi, visse 14 anni, 11 mesi e 15 giorni. Giulio Germano realizzò questo per la sua dolcissima figlia.</p>  </div>  <div id=\"commentary\"><h2>commentary</h2>  <p>The structure of the epitaph is the traditional one for pagan epitaphs, with the name of the deceased (and an attribute), his/her age, the name of the dedicant, a noun describing the deceased (which often expresses the degree of kinship with the dedicant) in dative and the dedication verb (<span class=\"lang\" lang=\"grc\">ποιέω</span> in the aorist form), for which see Korhonen (2004: 85-87). The attribute <span class=\"lang\" lang=\"grc\">θεοφιλής</span> attributed to the deceased is uncommon in pagan Greek epigraphy, more frequent in Christian epigraphy in the superlative form as an attribute of bishops and emperors.</p>  </div>  <div id=\"bibliography\"><h2>bibliography</h2>  <ul><li></li><li> Ferrara 1829 390 no. 3 <a href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10002005\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10002005</a>  </li><li> Kaibel 1890 <a href=\"https://clio.columbia.edu/catalog/6873760\" target=\"_blank\">480</a>  <a href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001072\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001072</a>  </li><li> Korhonen 2004 100 <a href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10000028\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10000028</a>  </li></ul>  <ul><li> Korhonen 2004 85-87 <a href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10000028\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10000028</a>  </li></ul>  </div>  <div id=\"handnote\"> <p>Rhomboid Ο, Θ, Φ; Α with broken bar. Presence of interpuncts and of a ligature of ΜΗ at l. 3</p> Lines 1-5  16-30  Interlineation line 1 to 2  not registered  </div><div id=\"license\"> Licensed under a Creative Commons-Attribution 4.0 licence. </div>",
